Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大人  莉科  还有艾克蕾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实今早我们和亲卫队帮果园摘了果子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想也分给阿雪你们尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就这么热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是勇者大人一行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首领
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯卡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位这是要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老朋友要来拜访我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娜  伊斯卡  好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的克雷托斯来接你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿代尔　瓦雷利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达尔基安卿和伊斯卡先生与那两位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应当说是很久以前的孽缘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:55.10,logo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(1030,550)\be60}「封印洞窟战！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当英雄王大人还作为勇者奔走在这片大地上时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首领和伊斯卡大人也是勇者团队的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者阿代尔与召唤出她的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王瓦雷利与锻冶师伊斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上年轻的剑豪希娜·玛齐西玛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娜…  伊斯卡先生也是这么称呼她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莉奥修·达尔基安这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是首领成为比斯科迪骑士的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被当时的领主殿下授予的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说这两个名字都很宝贵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也是第一次看到龙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷托斯也是勇者团队的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  今天他们是要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是去南方的弗莱泽沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是要去确认魔物的封印是否完好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这热度还是不减当年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷托斯  距离封印洞窟还差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也好久没来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地的精灵还精神着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我设下的封印刀看来都没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害  伊斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印在这里的魔物们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它们沉眠在封印之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它们回归到其原本应有的样子就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的理论没错的话注定会是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变化成为魔物  只不过是因为土地神或精灵生病而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要进行适当的治疗就一定能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔刀的魔物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要找出原因就能治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里采取的封印方式是让自然产生的魔物精灵化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验进行的很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就等着看成果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…其实本来不管魔物再怎么作乱都不关我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这道封印老化得很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3号封印  年代很久远了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  这魔物…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得是只大老鼠？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  是个很不好对付的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把剑当时也是把名剑  但…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3号封印损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为应对紧急情况  现封锁洞窟的部分区域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防止魔物逃离洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:05:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  这种事情也是有可能会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔物苏醒的话只要再封印起来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁它出来的瞬间解决它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印者请负责对付魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小老鼠？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样的魔物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠们  给我等一下  不可到处乱跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在封印的过程中分裂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是出人意料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总得抓住它们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天元·纺墓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成喵球了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说这群小家伙已经受到了佛罗尼之力的保佑？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们正处在精灵化的过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不再是魔物了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的夫妻  要高兴还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饮食习性和繁殖力都不明的半精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们依然很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娜  没办法说服它们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都饿昏了头  完全没办法进行交流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿代尔　瓦雷利！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的老鼠们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们俩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位都先…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娜  小心上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娜  过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿代尔  那可…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后座力太…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿代尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这里也并不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:09:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿代尔　瓦雷利  就没有什么对策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  魔王纹没法启动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娜也变成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了  只能请求支援了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有之前和勇者们建立的网络
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名为「勇气之绊」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:18.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,630)}Brave Connect
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的后辈们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿代尔大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的样子好像有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实现在我因为魔物的原因遭遇了点小危机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位勇者  能助我一臂之力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话不如大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是小动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请准备好网和笼子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有猎人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事出紧急  请把狩猎用具借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能帮上殿下的忙  尽管拿去用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的话什么都能找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘁  差不多快到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿代尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比斯科迪组准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽雷特&帕斯提亚久联合军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也做好了一切准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得太棒了  我亲爱的各位勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇气之绊  连接
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召唤法阵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊斯卡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿代尔大人们变得好小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连首领都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这数量好惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mercurius
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海  殿下  总之先解决这群老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大干一场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡  库蓓尔  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能被先祖大人所依靠真是开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有三位勇者殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  雪风  艾克蕾尔  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备…走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮子王苍雷破！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔罗牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡  干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话很快就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克蕾尔  阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大丰收大丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家伙儿没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分头去帮其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝琪  库蓓尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大家都缩小了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗心大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服和鞋子我用忍术设法解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太没面子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库大人  快把大家带去安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我和真久去把它们抓回来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  高尔  看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝石吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能保护你们两个的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  阿代尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上吧  高尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面应该是死路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真太让人费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  好大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变那么大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是老BOSS了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辉力炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Defender
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  高尔殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝琪  七海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么危险的魔物  怎么能让他们跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你摁到了抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鼠仔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然依靠偷来的生命力巨大化了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:16:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的不是那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和真久的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔物哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们用合体超必杀来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退治你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪雷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下封灭斩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  你怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.97,0:17:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高尔你才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么长时间才注意到！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以这种方式具现化了英雄结晶的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手头的结晶里出现了纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被刻印上去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这表明英雄结晶已经承认你们为其主人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说真久和殿下有着成为英雄的资质咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来  为什么我们还没有变回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不久后也会变回来的才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  高尔大人  好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不甘心  不过真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  果然比我要高很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只是七海你变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这情景怎么看怎么觉得诡异啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人欣慰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  变回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高尔大人  闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久  不能呆在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞎眼英雄指！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在下的忍术也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家才不重呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效果到期了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道会是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  衣服在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  眼睛  我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了  贝琪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气  要拐弯了  抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  不是这儿  能不能稍稍抓下别的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  很痒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  真久这状态的话  这感觉怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像犯罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯·罪！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  现在因为你这样子只是看上去有点像而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有这样那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠们还是再次被仔细封印了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不了太久  他们就会重生成土地神或者精灵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变回来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有点遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再等几年  两位就会变成那样子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  还是这样的真久比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.64,0:20:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算摸了你也不会再被当作犯罪者了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克蕾尔也来吧  快来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了大家  了结一事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多就是发生了这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你们能有福利享  不公平的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我一个人丢外面好寂寞的…说！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  实在太突然了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为补偿  我明天陪你玩个够好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:20:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾贝卡  长大了的真久很帅吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  实际上…相当帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想给公主殿下看看的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么样的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人的关系还是那么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与子孙在夜空下散步的感觉也挺不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不介意  我随时都可以陪你的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是倒了大楣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛还是好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你日常行径的报应呐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然管戳眼睛叫必杀技  还加了英雄之名  我说你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就使出了秘奥义…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.69,0:23:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  下集也请…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.24,0:23:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多关照了！
